channel.title: President Knockout Script
channel.description:
yea so im procrasinating doing h/w and its like 3:30am lol!, anyways i wondered off to miniclip.com and found president knockout so i made a simple script for it lol, here it is:
[Code]
{http://www.miniclip.com/games/presidential-knockout/en/} program new; var x,y,scar11,scar12:integer; procedure punchtype; begin case random(4) of 0: sendkeys('w')
1: sendkeys('a')
2: sendkeys('s')
3: sendkeys('d') end; end;
procedure loadbitmaps; begin scar11 := BitmapFromString(26, 8, 'z78DA8D5351AEC42008BC120' + '3DAEAA7A2DEFF488BD5E6D9F4B5BB9234141106672CE88B7E58CA' + '20506BDD7FFAAE6B4474C306BFC64B21B3B15B040CBE9C1272E44' + 'AED3985BF634B190161548B877FCF99BDA8E39F1894CC46AF7BE6' + 'FB4499D1D0B451357B5D638A1AA8DBD3AD7A78B8B5974D9410D74' + '8A8AC9C67F7FB6E102FB34248DDFF05DBBC93D71B4E460DDAC8DC' + '12EFBCEFC77744F6C685D5F0BB2BFEE1A7C01B6FD9B3639915C46' + '5977EE1F48F2F6A4F39B1A2426765EBC472E9AEC8C807BF72E19D' + 'BBDE8A218614D3257CCDD46DEC9A7AB07FE1B4AB575B7BCD49563' + '135262159E34309ABBA12DB0DD7F3B64D5765DD554281CEB3D97E' + 'F33BB658399FEC1C0ABFE46B457FBE6D322BB8CC60BAD25357935' + 'F1295A95BF3935C90C72A41F6A757F3F482A2EFCFFD29333A5397' + 'DCE70A6A4A3BB11D9CFEA399237EEFF8014452FEEE'); scar12 := BitmapFromString(12, 1, 'z78DA73767306424A8025180' + '000CB77135A'); end;
begin loadbitmaps; ActivateClient; wait(2000) repeat wait(50) punchtype; if(findbitmap(scar11,x,y))then begin KeyDown(32) wait(3000) KeyUp(32) end; until(iskeydown('q')) end.
[/Code]
have fun lol, can beat any level, easy, medium, or hard, to stop it, just hit "q"

item.title: President Knockout Script
item.dc:creator: @deathbyvirus deathbyvirus
item.description:
@deathbyvirus wrote:

yea so im procrasinating doing h/w and its like 3:30am lol!, anyways i wondered off to miniclip.com and found president knockout so i made a simple script for it lol, here it is:


{http://www.miniclip.com/games/presidential-knockout/en/}
program new;
var
 x,y,scar11,scar12:integer;
procedure punchtype;
begin
case random(4) of
 0: sendkeys('w')

 1: sendkeys('a')

 2: sendkeys('s')

 3: sendkeys('d')
 end;
end;

procedure loadbitmaps;
begin
  scar11 := BitmapFromString(26, 8, 'z78DA8D5351AEC42008BC120' +
       '3DAEAA7A2DEFF488BD5E6D9F4B5BB9234141106672CE88B7E58CA' +
       '20506BDD7FFAAE6B4474C306BFC64B21B3B15B040CBE9C1272E44' +
       'AED3985BF634B190161548B877FCF99BDA8E39F1894CC46AF7BE6' +
       'FB4499D1D0B451357B5D638A1AA8DBD3AD7A78B8B5974D9410D74' +
       '8A8AC9C67F7FB6E102FB34248DDFF05DBBC93D71B4E460DDAC8DC' +
       '12EFBCEFC77744F6C685D5F0BB2BFEE1A7C01B6FD9B3639915C46' +
       '5977EE1F48F2F6A4F39B1A2426765EBC472E9AEC8C807BF72E19D' +
       'BBDE8A218614D3257CCDD46DEC9A7AB07FE1B4AB575B7BCD49563' +
       '135262159E34309ABBA12DB0DD7F3B64D5765DD554281CEB3D97E' +
       'F33BB658399FEC1C0ABFE46B457FBE6D322BB8CC60BAD25357935' +
       'F1295A95BF3935C90C72A41F6A757F3F482A2EFCFFD29333A5397' +
       'DCE70A6A4A3BB11D9CFEA399237EEFF8014452FEEE');
  scar12 := BitmapFromString(12, 1, 'z78DA73767306424A8025180' +
       '000CB77135A');
end;

begin
loadbitmaps;
ActivateClient;
wait(2000)
  repeat
 wait(50)
 punchtype;
 if(findbitmap(scar11,x,y))then
  begin
    KeyDown(32)
    wait(3000)
    KeyUp(32)
  end;
 until(iskeydown('q'))
end.

have fun lol, can beat any level, easy, medium, or hard, to stop it, just hit “q”
